{
  "stem": "268.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're getting into-- into the painful part of-- of my recollections now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The director who-- who was-- worked in a factory-- and as I described him before, he was a mean looking guy, but yet he was a-- he was a human being, as it later turned out.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two or three times when they grabbed us in the ghetto, he would come in-- come to the police headquarters and argue with them and got us out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The last time-- the one before last-- yeah-- he-- yeah, they took us  in this sierociniec-- in this orphanage building.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were shipping up-- shipping out in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At dawn, this guy comes in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as we were separated-- men separate, women separate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I see somebody standing there and gesticulating with his hands and arms and speaking with the-- with the SS people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he kept saying, I got to have them with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do you mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, really shouting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he would call out our names.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He would see all of-- next thing I know, somebody takes a list and calls names and tell us, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Out of formation, to the right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he took us out again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to-- and my-- so it's my brother, myself, and I.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But our-- my mother was still to the left with the other women.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my brother did a-- did a heroic act.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was-- you know, stepping up to an SS man, who has like a baseball bat in his hand, you know, who is hitting left and right for any miscue-- for any misstep, he would [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He would step up at-- and stand at attention.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was fluent in German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was very bright.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He spoke good German.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
